body_html: I encounter almost the same problem as you. My OS is mac Sierra. I saved a model as pbtxt file of which size is 800M. However, when I want to freeze it with freeze_graph.py, the python process is always killed by the system and there are no useful logs printed by the system. I debug the python program and find the crash always when google.protobuf.text_format.Merge is executed. But I don't know why.
